.TH FCHMODAT 2 2012-05-22 "Linux" "Linux Programmerz Manual"
.SH NAME
fchmodat \- chizzle permissionz of a gangbangin' file relatizzle ta a gangbangin' finger-lickin' directory \
file descriptor
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
.BR "#include <fcntl.h>" "           /* Definizzle of AT_* constants */"
.B #include <sys/stat.h>
